e.Ok so after  some more gameplay:First thing i want to talk about is i went and put away the joystick and am trying the x-box 360 controller. So far it seems to be a bit smoother and more easy then my js but i notice that i can not bind the key 100% to my likings. Ex. The num-pad i am unable to bind any key to these and thats a big issue even if you do just up down left right thats 4 keys your missing out on as well as 4 more if you go NE SE SW NW as well. So that is one thing that can be greatly improved. Also this duel joystick type controller (x-box360) if at all possible would be nice too to have it move your crosshairs around the screen or be centerd to ship as well as i mention on js.Another thing i would like to ask about and maybe suggest is straff comands. This seems like such a important part of space flying and maneuverability. If these commands are intended to be left out please let me know if just not thought of that would be a great fix to the flying and maneuverability of your ships."
