 within the world you really should pick it up. For the rest I would recommend videos.. Watch gameplay videos and if you still feel it's something you'd be willing to play than do it.Post release: I really wanted to try again, it's Jan 2015 and there is a campaign. Unfortunately the UI is still there, it's still a lot like flying an underwater fighter plane and this is completely on me but I can't get through the tutorial screens. They literally pop up a new set of tutorials immediately as you close the previous screen. Want to get familiar with the flight controls they just explained? Okay, let's exit and try them out BLAM Tutorial- Time to talk about menu functions.. Still trying to get the hang of the flight instructions but okay, well lets see if I remember how to remap those abilities BLAM Tutorial - Let's talk a little about map functionality.. C'mon I almost actually learned something!.. And this goes on for 100's of tutorial items without pause."
